'''碳酸镭'''是一种无机化合物，化学式为RaCO<sub>3</sub>，有强放射性。它可以形成正交晶系晶体，空间群''Pmcn''。<ref>Weigel, F.; Trinkl, A. Crystal chemistry of radium.  V.  Radium salts of inorganic anions. ''Radiochimica Acta'', 1973. 19 (4): 199-202. ISSN: 0033-8230.</ref>
==制备==
碳酸镭可以通过可溶性镭盐和[[碳酸铵|碳酸铵]]反应得到：<ref name=Richard>Richard C. Ropp. Encyclopedia of the Alkaline Earth Compounds. Elsevier, 2013. pp 370-371. Radium Carbonate</ref>
: Ra<sup>2+</sup> + CO<sub>3</sub><sup>2-</sup> → RaCO<sub>3</sub>↓

[[硫酸镭|硫酸镭]]和1.5 M[[碳酸钠|碳酸钠]]在85 °C反应，也能得到碳酸镭。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Radioanalytical and Nuclear Chemistry|volume=310|issue=2|language=en|issn=0236-5731|date=2016-11|pages=589–595|doi=10.1007/s10967-016-4927-x|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s10967-016-4927-x|title=Disassembly of old radium sources and conversion of radium sulfate into radium carbonate for subsequent dissolution in acid|accessdate=2020-12-10|author=Artem V. Matyskin, Burçak Ebin, Mikhail Tyumentsev, Stefan Allard, Gunnar Skarnemark, Henrik Ramebäck, Christian Ekberg}}</ref>
==性质及用途==
碳酸镭可以和酸反应，生成其它镭化合物：
: RaCO<sub>3</sub> + 2 HNO<sub>3</sub> → Ra(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub> + 2 H<sub>2</sub>O

在室温时，碳酸镭在[[碳酸铵|碳酸铵]]或[[氯化铵|氯化铵]]浓溶液中的溶解度比[[碳酸钡|碳酸钡]]大10倍，借此可将镭与钡分离。<ref>Nikitin, B. A. Studies on the analytical chemistry of radium. II. Reactions of pure radium. ''Trav. inst. elat radium (U. S. S. R.)'', 1937. 3. pp 228-237. CAN31: 32676.</ref>它可用于制造镭铍中子源。<ref>Bedrich, Fridrich. Preparation of radium-​beryllium neutron sources. ''Sb. Ref. Celostatni Radiochem. Konf., 3, Liblice, Czech.'', 1964. pp 135. CAN64: 90519.</ref>
